* Print bar codes on a Laser printer
* for Avery 5160 10x3 labels
columns             3
top margin          1
line length         84lines/inch          6* Page Layout/Format
*Page length         60
records/page        30
select              Bib
>=                  ?Enter lowest bib number desired
and
select              Bib
<=                  ?Enter maximum bib number desired
labels
form feed at end
